    "span": "The Warden lives and is in good health; she will address the outpost herself at dusk.",
    "issue": "Directly contradicts the guard's assertion that the Warden fell three nights ago; warden status is inconsistent across speakers (C-narrative-warden-status-consistency)."
  },
  {
    "span": "between the two of us — the Warden fell three nights ago. The elders simply haven't said so aloud yet.",
    "issue": "Reveals the Warden's death before the elders have publicly disclosed it, potentially a premature spoiler (C-narrative-no-premature-spoiler)."
  }
]

